{"tid":668310,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[腳膠]難忍連詩雅長腿誘惑 洋腸大叔喪影腳","createTime":"2018-05-17T13:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T13:10:20.000Z","uid":157545,"like":251,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9417b2cb8ec58cbdae1bedc4278529e2800546","tid":668310,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526304534_2041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526304534_2041.jpg&h=34d64b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連詩雅、鄭欣宜、鄧健泓同羅霖最近拍緊網劇《性敢中環》，顧名思義，呢套網劇就係講喺中環發生嗁事，戲中連詩雅扮演一名心理醫生，日前，《蘋果》見佢喺中環拍攝一場佢同好姊妹雨僑爭仔後鬧交，連詩雅獨自落老蘭買醉，飲到high晒離開，仲要喺街上嘔。<br />\n<br />\n拍攝當晚8點幾，着住露腰裝配貼身牛仔褲兼4吋高踭鞋嘅連詩雅，倚住欄杆拍攝，劇情交待佢街頭醉酒玩電話，睇完電話短訊即刻嬲到怒掟手機，臨近晚飯時間喺中環拍戲，少不免都會吸引好多巿民圍觀，其中有一名外籍男子仲拎住手機喪影，呢位外籍男子似乎有戀足癖，透過佢部電話睇到，全部照片都係大特寫影連詩雅膝頭以下小腿位置，仲立即同朋友開心share，將相片放去朋友群組，同時露出猥瑣笑容。好彩連詩雅當日係着牛仔褲，唔係短裙，而呢一鏡都係拍攝尾聲，佢拍完就好快收工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《性敢中環》劇日前中午又到上環出外景，呢次就熱鬧好多，有鄧健泓、欣宜同埋客串嘅羅霖，劇情交待任職教師嘅欣宜發現鄧健泓疑似跟蹤佢，欣宜向羅霖求助。拍攝期間，鄧健泓唔停咁玩電話，唔知佢係咪向老婆石詠莉報到。52歲「美魔女」羅霖雖同本月30日牛一就31歲嘅欣宜年齡相差21歲，不過佢哋合作開工都冇代溝，全程有傾有講，欣宜仲搵劇組工作人員代拎手機合照留念。佔戲唔多嘅羅霖相當受劇組歡迎，佢完戲份離開時，仲好親切逐一跟幕後人員say拜拜，大家又要求佢集郵，羅霖有求必應，睇嚟佢真係好有人緣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526304536_3b57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526304536_3b57.jpg&h=f9f16a01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526304542_cb65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526304542_cb65.jpg&h=5f934ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526304544_c48b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526304544_c48b.jpg&h=dc5d4454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180514/large/1526304547_08f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180514%2Flarge%2F1526304547_08f1.jpg&h=fbce1df0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c28019ed786e74a17f99750929d677ab0ce8d607","tid":668310,"uid":56321,"like":157,"dislike":4,"score":153,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔都有鬼佬？"},{"pid":"b1f0735336263845ec2ab969ad1460e512edca37","tid":668310,"uid":27597,"like":167,"dislike":8,"score":159,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:32:10.000Z","msg":"白溝靚腳既女女著依款鞋真係最撚正"},{"pid":"5ae23c583037759affed94bbedb3c78206dbe8df","tid":668310,"uid":143288,"like":92,"dislike":1,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:32:37.000Z","msg":"長褲都好影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd61750d203fe4a953d78b3f31d66f49d94d9d5","tid":668310,"uid":50328,"like":12,"dislike":24,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:32:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5232abed0228b2de52f56ba147ed508abc36b41c","tid":668310,"uid":35930,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:33:20.000Z","msg":"老貓本尊"},{"pid":"d3d7f700d3827c0128827e5bd9c6a6455625740c","tid":668310,"uid":67896,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"唔係着緊長褲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n影腳掌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a60633dc6122917a0337d10a93a9bcb503a9265","tid":668310,"uid":46195,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:39:17.000Z","msg":"有咩好影"},{"pid":"fb75b936d9257509404003ea2bb6e66c19e43cd4","tid":668310,"uid":67500,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:40:07.000Z","msg":"阿凡達對腳仲長啦"},{